Introduction

Welcome to Book Bounty, your Ultimate Book Companion. At Book Bounty, we prioritize your privacy and aim to provide a secure and enjoyable reading experience. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your 
information when you use our mobile application ("Book Bounty").

By using Book Bounty, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, please refrain from using the App.

Information Collection

Book Bounty does not collect any personal information from its users. We neither request nor store any personal data, including but not limited to names, email addresses, or location information.

AI Assistant Interaction

While using our AI Assistant, please note that interactions with the AI are not stored or associated with individual users. We do not retain any data related to these interactions.

Data Security

Although we do not collect personal information, we take security seriously. Our App is designed to protect your privacy. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. 
We cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy in the future, reflecting any changes in our practices or for operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy within the App.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at Berrtado@icloud.com. Your privacy matters to us, and we are here to address any inquiries you may have.

Thank you for choosing Book Bounty, your Ultimate Book Companion!
